  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech的AI Agent协作流程画一个架构图，核心是Architecture as Code的落地。我想把DiagnosticEngine作为整个流程的起点，因为它是我们最关键的推理引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "PO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，DiagnosticEngine作为入口。那它直接对接下游哪些组件？我注意到HIPAA_Vault在合规层面很重要，是不是应该让它承担中心协调的角色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，HIPAA_Vault确实要做成枢纽。不过这里有个细节——Design Team里的架构师节点也叫HIPAA_Vault，但职责不同：PM那个是合规中枢，ARCH那个是设计侧的Vault代理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "PM",
        "ARCH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "理解了，同名不同职责。那我把Design Team做成一个子图，里面放ARCH和DES两个节点。DES用EMR_Sync来对接电子病历同步，这样层级关系更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Design Team",
        "ARCH",
        "DES",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。Development Team那边也需要独立子图，DEV同样用EMR_Sync，但和DES是上下游关系——DES输出设计规范，DEV负责开发实现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Development Team",
        "DEV",
        "DES",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Dev Team里除了DEV，还需要QA环节吧？我看到PatientRecords这个组件，是不是QC质检节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "QC"
